title: Wow. This lady learnt Finnish! 😱 Finnish-Peruvian's Finnish Language Journey ✨

media:group.media:title: Wow. This lady learnt Finnish! 😱 Finnish-Peruvian's Finnish Language Journey ✨
media:group.media:description:
Sometimes the journey to learning Finnish never ends.... 🤣

I invited my friend Isabella for a chat on my channel about her story and her thoughts about learning Finnish. We discussed topics such as: when she moved to Finland, when did she actually start feeling more comfortable with Finnish, her tips for learning Finnish, Finnish grammar and her most used Finnish phrases.
